human at all.

81
00:04:15,655 --> 00:04:16,656
-Well, of course not.

82
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:18,158
That's why they call
it a Beast Spirit.

83
00:04:18,158 --> 00:04:19,226
Isn't it obvious?

84
00:04:19,259 --> 00:04:20,827
-But it's like Takuya
isn't even in there.

85
00:04:20,894 --> 00:04:22,062
Can't we help him?

86
00:04:22,095 --> 00:04:23,663
-Not really.

87
00:04:23,663 --> 00:04:25,499
