Beast Spirit on his own.

88
00:04:25,499 --> 00:04:26,967
Sooner or later, he will.

89
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,702
-It's the later part
I'm worried about.

90
00:04:28,702 --> 00:04:32,539
[shouting]

91
