-(THINKING) This is
just like before.

98
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,424
Back in the real world.

99
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:58,198
BOY (OFFSCREEN):
Come on, guys.

100
00:04:58,231 --> 00:04:59,533
Knock it off!

101
00:04:59,566 --> 00:05:01,601
Hey!

102
00:05:01,601 --> 00:05:02,969
BOY (OFFSCREEN): Aw, did the
baby drop his books?

103
00:05:03,003 --> 00:05:05,305
Next thing you know, he's
gonna fall down.

104
00:05:05,338 --> 00:05:07,274
-Quit it!

105
