-You're a wimp, kid!

108
00:05:12,779 --> 00:05:14,114
Look, there's another baby!

109
00:05:14,147 --> 00:05:15,248
-Oh, no!

110
00:05:18,451 --> 00:05:19,986
BOY (OFFSCREEN): Better
run, kid!

111
00:05:20,053 --> 00:05:21,421
-(THINKING) But what can I do?

112
00:05:21,454 --> 00:05:22,956
Those kids were bigger
than me, and

113
00:05:22,989 --> 00:05:25,325
BurningGreymon is way bigger.

114
00:05:25,392 --> 00:05:26,426
Takuya, no!

115
00:05:35,067 --> 00:05:36,669
ZOE (OFFSCREEN): Tommy!

116
00:05:36,669 --> 00:05:38,337
-(THINKING) I'm not just gonna
stand by this time.

117
00:05:43,509 --> 00:05:45,377
Takuya!

118
00:05:45,411 --> 00:05:47,346
Please, you've gotta
stop this!

119
