-Tommy, you have to stop this.

137
00:06:40,999 --> 00:06:42,968
-My name is Kumamon, and you're

138
00:06:43,001 --> 00:06:45,571
nothing but a big bully.

139
00:06:45,637 --> 00:06:46,905
-No, you're wrong.

140
00:06:46,972 --> 00:06:48,807
-Kumamon, you're under
the spell of

