isn't paying bullies back.

146
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,655
It's just standing up to them.

147
00:07:03,689 --> 00:07:06,125
You helped me see that fighting
back in fear is just

148
00:07:06,158 --> 00:07:07,659
as bad as being a bully.

149
00:07:07,659 --> 00:07:08,794
You can't let fear
control you.

150
00:07:08,827 --> 00:07:10,129
You have to fight it.

151
00:07:13,265 --> 00:07:15,801
