-Agunimon!

264
00:12:31,848 --> 00:12:32,815
Ah!

265
00:12:32,849 --> 00:12:34,984
-Gigasmon, put him down!

266
00:12:35,017 --> 00:12:39,322
-If you want him, you
have come take him!

267
00:12:39,388 --> 00:12:41,157
-Don't worry, we're fine now.

268
00:12:41,224 --> 00:12:42,658
I mean, we're kind
of stuck here.

269
00:12:42,725 --> 00:12:43,993
-OK.

270
00:12:47,763 --> 00:12:49,565
GIGASMON (OFFSCREEN): If play
hide and seek, you really need

271
00:12:49,599 --> 00:12:50,867
seek, you know?

272
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:04,881
-Tommy!

273
00:13:08,551 --> 00:13:09,552
-Not bad.

274
00:13:09,585 --> 00:13:12,555
Course, not good, either.

275
00:13:12,555 --> 00:13:13,890
-When I get my hands on you!

276
00:13:18,227 --> 00:13:19,529
-No!

277
00:13:23,432 --> 00:13:24,433
-Agunimon!

278
00:13:24,433 --> 00:13:26,769
[screaming]

279
00:13:26,802 --> 00:13:27,804
-Yeah, you tough guy.

280
00:13:27,837 --> 00:13:29,772
Ha ha ha!

281
00:13:29,805 --> 00:13:31,741
-No!

282
00:13:31,774 --> 00:13:34,610
This is gonna hurt!

283
00:13:34,644 --> 00:13:35,611
-Oh, no!

284
00:13:35,611 --> 00:13:36,946
-Oh, my!

285
00:13:36,946 --> 00:13:37,980
-I was right.

286
00:13:42,451 --> 00:13:43,286
-Takuya!

287
00:13:43,286 --> 00:13:45,988
-Are you OK?

288
00:13:46,055 --> 00:13:47,123
-Yeah.

289
00:13:47,190 --> 00:13:49,025
But Tommy's still in trouble,
and I don't

290
00:13:49,058 --> 00:13:50,359
know how to save him.

291
00:13:50,393 --> 00:13:52,595
-Looks like a Human Spirit
just can't compete with a

292
00:13:52,628 --> 00:13:53,963
Beast Spirit.

293
00:13:53,963 --> 00:13:56,032
You back to turn into
BurningGreymon.

294
00:13:56,065 --> 00:13:57,333
-But I can't.

295
00:13:57,333 --> 00:14:00,002
What if I lose control again?

296
00:14:00,036 --> 00:14:00,836
ZOE (OFFSCREEN): Don't
be afraid.

297
00:14:00,836 --> 00:14:03,005
Just remember what Tommy said.

298
00:14:03,005 --> 00:14:04,340
-Huh?

299
00:14:04,373 --> 00:14:07,677
-I learned that true courage
isn't paying bullies back,

300
00:14:07,677 --> 00:14:10,346
it's just standing up to them.

301
00:14:10,379 --> 00:14:12,648
You helped me see that fighting
back in fear is just

302
00:14:12,682 --> 00:14:14,016
as bad as being a bully.

303
00:14:14,016 --> 00:14:15,651
You can't let fear
control you.

304
00:14:15,685 --> 00:14:16,986
You have to fight it.

305
00:14:19,789 --> 00:14:23,025
I know you won't hurt me if you
remember we're friends.

306
00:14:23,092 --> 00:14:25,027
-Wait.

307
00:14:25,094 --> 00:14:26,329
Tommy?

308
00:14:26,362 --> 00:14:27,530
ZOE (OFFSCREEN): Remember
who your friends are,

309
00:14:27,530 --> 00:14:29,265
and you'll be fine.

310
00:14:29,298 --> 00:14:30,166
-What?

311
00:14:30,233 --> 00:14:33,569
Not want to help friend?

312
00:14:33,569 --> 00:14:35,238
-Tommy!

313
00:14:35,271 --> 00:14:36,739
-Ha ha ha!

314
00:14:36,739 --> 00:14:39,742
Play time over, now
give me spirit.

315
00:14:39,742 --> 00:14:44,213
You hurry, maybe you save him.

316
00:14:44,247 --> 00:14:45,748
-No, don't do it, Takuya!

317
00:14:45,748 --> 00:14:47,950
Don't trade your
spirit for me!

318
00:14:48,017 --> 00:14:51,220
It's OK. I'm not afraid!

319
00:14:51,254 --> 00:14:52,421
No!

320
00:14:52,421 --> 00:14:52,989
GIGASMON (OFFSCREEN): Hm.

321
00:14:53,022 --> 00:14:55,057
Some friend you be.

322
00:14:55,091 --> 00:14:58,160
Won't even give up Beast
Spirit to save friend.

323
00:14:58,194 --> 00:14:59,395
-I'm not afraid of you!

324
00:14:59,428 --> 00:15:02,732
-You should be.

325
00:15:02,798 --> 00:15:06,669
[shouting]

326
00:15:06,702 --> 00:15:07,303
-No!

327
00:15:07,336 --> 00:15:08,671
Tommy!

328
00:15:08,704 --> 00:15:10,139
That's it!

329
00:15:10,172 --> 00:15:11,641
If Tommy can show courage
in the face of that

330
00:15:11,674 --> 00:15:13,476
freak, then so can I!

331
00:15:22,485 --> 00:15:23,819
-Execute!

332
00:15:23,853 --> 00:15:25,154
Beast Spirit Evolution!

333
00:15:28,824 --> 00:15:32,128
[screaming]

334
00:15:43,372 --> 00:15:45,708
-BurningGreymon!

335
00:15:45,708 --> 00:15:50,046
-So, let's see if can control.

336
00:15:50,046 --> 00:15:51,080
-Takuya!

337
00:15:57,053 --> 00:15:58,054
-Whoa!

338
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:03,959
GIGASMON (OFFSCREEN):
Not going make it!

339
00:16:16,382 --> 00:16:18,183
-Tommy, you OK?

340
00:16:18,217 --> 00:16:18,951
-Yeah.

341
00:16:19,018 --> 00:16:20,352
Hey, check it out!

342
00:16:20,386 --> 00:16:23,088
You got control of your
Beast Spirit.

343
00:16:23,122 --> 00:16:24,256
-Thanks to you, buddy.

344
00:16:24,290 --> 00:16:25,491
-I'll help the others.

345
00:16:25,491 --> 00:16:26,659
Now go get him!

346
00:16:26,659 --> 00:16:27,860
-Right!

347
00:16:30,729 --> 00:16:33,332
You're the one who likes
twisters, right?

348
00:16:33,365 --> 00:16:34,366
Well, enjoy!

349
00:16:44,677 --> 00:16:45,544
-That fun!

350
00:16:45,611 --> 00:16:46,979
Now your turn!

351
00:16:51,183 --> 00:16:52,184
-Pyro--

352
00:16:52,251 --> 00:16:54,353
wait, I'll set fire to
the whole forest.

353
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:55,921
OK, I'll do it the old
fashioned way.

354
00:17:03,729 --> 00:17:04,930
Execute!

355
00:17:06,298 --> 00:17:07,599
Slide Evolution!

356
00:17:11,904 --> 00:17:12,905
Agunimon!

357
00:17:20,346 --> 00:17:22,614
I have to lead him away
from the others.

358
00:17:22,681 --> 00:17:23,983
Tag, you're it!

359
00:17:29,588 --> 00:17:31,156
What's the matter, slowpoke?

360
00:17:31,190 --> 00:17:32,558
Can't you catch me?

361
00:17:39,465 --> 00:17:40,666
Hey, Gigasmon.

362
00:17:40,699 --> 00:17:43,001
You're not getting tired
now, are ya?

363
00:17:43,035 --> 00:17:44,636
[panting]

364
00:17:44,670 --> 00:17:47,973
-You gotta start working
out, buddy.

365
00:17:48,006 --> 00:17:53,612
-Even if me tired, you still
get defeated good.

366
00:17:53,645 --> 00:17:57,816
Did you forget me warrior
of earth?

367
00:17:57,883 --> 00:18:00,152
-Actually, I did forget
about that.

368
00:18:00,219 --> 00:18:01,286
-Tectonic Slam!

369
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:07,192
-Oh, man!

370
00:18:07,192 --> 00:18:08,193
-Ha ha ha!

371
00:18:11,530 --> 00:18:12,631
-What are you excited about?

372
00:18:12,698 --> 00:18:14,700
You missed me, earth boy.

373
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:17,202
By the way, I think you
forgot something, too.

374
00:18:17,236 --> 00:18:18,337
Execute!

375
00:18:21,206 --> 00:18:22,207
Slide Evolution!

376
00:18:26,478 --> 00:18:28,380
BurningGreymon!

377
00:18:28,414 --> 00:18:31,383
Out here there's no forest
to catch fire.

378
00:18:31,383 --> 00:18:32,951
-Uh-oh.

379
00:18:32,985 --> 00:18:34,053
-Pyro Barrage!

380
00:18:39,925 --> 00:18:40,926
Wildfire Tsunami!

381
00:18:50,769 --> 00:18:51,970
-You did it!

382
00:18:59,878 --> 00:19:01,814
BOKOMON (OFFSCREEN):
Gigasmon's spirit.

383
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:03,782
-And now for Tommy's.

384
00:19:03,849 --> 00:19:05,417
Here ya go, buddy.

385
00:19:05,451 --> 00:19:06,685
Got a little present for ya.

386
00:19:10,222 --> 00:19:13,025
-Hey, my spirit.

387
00:19:13,058 --> 00:19:14,359
Yeah!

388
00:19:14,393 --> 00:19:16,094
This is better than birthdays
and Christmas combine!

389
00:19:16,161 --> 00:19:17,663
-And now to get Zoe's spirit.

390
00:19:20,399 --> 00:19:23,635
-Hm?

391
00:19:23,669 --> 00:19:27,005
-Me leave while behind!

392
00:19:27,005 --> 00:19:28,674
-No!

393
00:19:28,707 --> 00:19:30,008
He still has my spirit.

394
00:19:37,699 --> 00:19:39,601
GRUMBLEMON (OFFSCREEN): Can't
believe me get spirit taken.

395
00:19:39,601 --> 00:19:42,737
Me make kids pay, and
pay big time.

396
00:19:42,771 --> 00:19:44,239
RANAMON (OFFSCREEN): Goodie.

397
00:19:44,272 --> 00:19:45,807
The beast with brains of dirt
has another incompetent plan.

398
00:19:45,807 --> 00:19:48,343
Honey, you couldn't
outwit a nitwit.

399
00:19:48,376 --> 00:19:48,977
-What?

400
00:19:49,010 --> 00:19:49,511
Who there?

401
00:19:49,544 --> 00:19:50,845
That you, Ranamon?

402
00:19:50,879 --> 00:19:54,682
-How many warriors of
water do you know?

403
00:19:54,716 --> 00:19:56,518
Now listen up, rockhead.

404
00:19:56,551 --> 00:19:58,953
Stop sneaking around behind our
backs trying to impress

405
00:19:58,987 --> 00:19:59,821
Cherubimon.

406
00:19:59,821 --> 00:20:01,156
-You back off.

407
00:20:01,189 --> 00:20:03,358
What I do no business of you.

408
00:20:03,425 --> 00:20:04,959
MERCURYMON (OFFSCREEN):
Thou art mistaken.

409
00:20:04,993 --> 00:20:05,860
GRUMBLEMON (OFFSCREEN):
Mercurymon.

410
00:20:05,927 --> 00:20:07,529
Warrior of steel.

411
00:20:07,595 --> 00:20:10,732
-Thy thoughtless acts reflect
badly upon us.

412
00:20:10,765 --> 00:20:13,835
Thou should study an opponent
first, not just boorishly rush

413
00:20:13,835 --> 00:20:14,569
into battle.

414
00:20:14,602 --> 00:20:16,137
-Got that right.

415
00:20:16,171 --> 00:20:17,972
GRUMBLEMON (OFFSCREEN):
Arbormon, warrior of wood.

416
00:20:18,006 --> 00:20:20,375
-Yo, you want I should rough
'em up for ya's?

417
00:20:20,375 --> 00:20:21,209
-Enough.

418
00:20:21,242 --> 00:20:22,544
Our circle is complete.

419
00:20:22,544 --> 00:20:24,312
-But Duskmon, warrior
of darkness--

420
00:20:24,379 --> 00:20:27,715
-Oh, sugar, he wouldn't join
us in a million years.

421
00:20:27,715 --> 00:20:29,350
-Forsooth.

422
00:20:29,384 --> 00:20:30,585
He hath no heart for battle,
and does little more than

423
00:20:30,618 --> 00:20:32,220
stare at the moons.

424
00:20:32,220 --> 00:20:35,223
We shall rule this world, whilst
his only domain shall

425
00:20:35,256 --> 00:20:37,725
be the world he sees when
he closeth his eyes.

426
00:20:37,759 --> 00:20:39,260
[laughter]

427
00:20:39,327 --> 00:20:40,762
GRUMBLEMON (OFFSCREEN):
Me no get.

428
00:20:40,829 --> 00:20:44,771
-Ugh, I'm surrounded
by buffoons.

429
00:20:44,771 --> 00:20:46,272
TOMMY (OFFSCREEN): Isn't
that pretty?

430
00:20:46,339 --> 00:20:48,942
ZOE (OFFSCREEN):
Yeah, I guess.

431
00:20:48,942 --> 00:20:50,443
-Come on, guys.

432
00:20:50,443 --> 00:20:54,180
We've got a long road
ahead of us.

433
00:20:54,214 --> 00:20:55,348
NARRATOR: That's for sure.

434
00:20:55,382 --> 00:20:56,249
They barely beat Gigasmon,
and now there are

435
00:20:56,316 --> 00:20:57,584
four other bad guys?

436
00:20:57,651 --> 00:20:59,953
This could get ugly on the next

437
00:20:59,986 --> 00:21:02,689
Digimon, Digital Monsters.

